{"tid":1668223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術台】討論下點樣令水魔法普及化","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T15:15:39.000Z","uid":310015,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d7fe806614e781a7cf0326bfb6b18de622a76c","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"近排出現咗大廈室內舖唔用火魔法嘅風向，因為火勢難控制，好易殃及池魚<br />\n個個都話水魔法門檻低，究竟<span style=\"color: gold;\">新手可以點樣準備</span>？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水魔法種類？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">漆彈</span>：阻擋狗狗視野，但需要<span style=\"color: red;\">掟中面罩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黏彈</span>：出發點同屎彈相近，令狗狗全日癡笠笠<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">油彈</span>：掟易燃物料，令佢更<span style=\"color: red;\">怕火</span>，唔會主動接近手足或開槍（有火花）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">腐蝕彈</span>：彈如其名，高酸或鹼性液體，<span style=\"color: red;\">傷害值最高</span>，但易整親自己，以下開放討論改善方法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應用甚麼容器盛載通渠水幫狗狗沖涼？<br />\n之前有手足用水槍射，結果側漏整親自己。<br />\n玻璃樽普遍要落地先爆到，咁就冇咗通渠水嘅意義<br />\n未諗到合適容器<br />\n所以暫時可以喺<span style=\"color: gold;\">制高點</span>例如天橋，擰開蓋一鳩倒落去，速逃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甚麼情況下使用？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">突襲、偷襲、群攻、遠攻、神獸休班警</span>時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非如何幫手準備素材？<br />\n呢樣講咗太耐，<span style=\"color: red;\">顏料、水彈（類似氣球嘅塑膠）、膠袋、麵粉、油、漏斗</span>等等，揀一兩樣帶過去啦，一定有用<br />\n甚至同friend夾定一人帶幾樣，去到即場入/溝<br />\n新職業解鎖！<span style=\"color: gold;\">水魔法調製員</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為前一晚整會難運送，俾狗周到又難解釋<br />\n一支油/通渠水易收埋，唔會自爆，搜到都一撚定告唔入"},{"pid":"092fa79f608d0af5fc1f91da04d7bc010440cc1c","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:17:53.000Z","msg":"一齊討論下點樣改良<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad4dfa4e203955bd16579050fb37667367bb545","tid":1668223,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"聖水點用？"},{"pid":"d73026a635367fa8aeb46b1fced4e8b91666d93d","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ad4dfa4e203955bd16579050fb37667367bb545","tid":1668223,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"聖水點用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:22:30.000Z","msg":"攻擊狗好好用<br />\n之前臥底狗中汽油彈都係燒咗一陣，傷害不大<br />\n如果有聖水掟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畫面好睇又傷害值高"},{"pid":"39e84ec8b025710ec1907c077f07fb9084474c02","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"同埋如果有制高點，聖水係<span style=\"color: gold;\">好好用</span><br />\n有幾可天橋會有單車/重物？<br />\n自己搬上去晒時間，又顯眼<br />\n有支通渠水喺手就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擰蓋，掉，完。"},{"pid":"7ed9810b4b4258fc0834462086d38e2200d8532c","tid":1668223,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"明明聖水比火魔容易<br />\n但偏偏冇人玩"},{"pid":"04d2491daeb50f9f7a797cbd4477dee20eb24bcc","tid":1668223,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:55:36.000Z","msg":"G chi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34475b6ca769f320cb8db6515e17e2fbff2c018","tid":1668223,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:58:05.000Z","msg":"所有男前線, 出手前10小時唔準去廁所.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99e5fe72f577c5283474c9a73fc09b524a5ee0f","tid":1668223,"uid":268178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d34475b6ca769f320cb8db6515e17e2fbff2c018","tid":166822