 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98f76e23986bac024ee9d6c1e07ea5d66209c97","tid":1668223,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e84ec8b025710ec1907c077f07fb9084474c02","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"同埋如果有制高點，聖水係<span style=\"color: gold;\">好好用</span><br />\n有幾可天橋會有單車/重物？<br />\n自己搬上去晒時間，又顯眼<br />\n有支通渠水喺手就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擰蓋，掉，完。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"制高點似乎比較適合用水魔法，但命中頭頂，就未必有減低視野效果，其他效果仍有。<br />\n同一水平，水魔法有效範圍太短，施法者不太安全，有無方法增水魔法距離同時不減少命中率呢？"},{"pid":"7956d4c91f5ac732b0411c8cc8bd985a691b9ab5","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e98f76e23986bac024ee9d6c1e07ea5d66209c97","tid":1668223,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e84ec8b025710ec1907c077f07fb9084474c02","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"同埋如果有制高點，聖水係<span style=\"color: gold;\">好好用</span><br />\n有幾可天橋會有單車/重物？<br />\n自己搬上去晒時間，又顯眼<br />\n有支通渠水喺手就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擰蓋，掉，完。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"制高點似乎比較適合用水魔法，但命中頭頂，就未必有減低視野效果，其他效果仍有。<br />\n同一水平，水魔法有效範圍太短，施法者不太安全，有無方法增水魔法距離同時不減少命中率呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"Exactly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水魔法樽頸位喺射程同命中率<br />\n<br />\n橡筋炮台可能有效，雖然命中率都唔高，但可以數量搭救"},{"pid":"a559a63d9505223c8bdc0734718050f9c7d0b12e","tid":1668223,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"370cfad52bd297b65225b640ea7779cbe4f153bf","tid":1668223,"uid":310015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a42de3750c314adda36e333a0e100a8f952718","tid":1668223,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d7fe806614e781a7cf0326bfb6b18de622a76c","tid":1668223,"uid